import { Image } from "@chakra-ui/image";
import { Box, Flex, Heading, Text } from "@chakra-ui/layout";





export default function QuemSomos() {
    
    return(
        <Box height="100%" >
          
            <Box position="relative" mt="45px" maxW="1367px" >
                <Flex justifyContent="space-around" >
                    <Box textAlign="center">
                        <Heading
                        fontWeight="bold"
                        fontSize="26px"
                        lineHeight="30px"
                        color="#454545"
                        >
                            Quem somos
                        </Heading>
                        <Text
                        mt="20px"
                        fontWeight="500"
                        fontSize="18px"
                        lineHeight="21px"
                        color="#575757"
                        >
                            Conheça a equipe por trás da produção da plataforma GoTokens.
                        </Text>
                        <Flex mt="90px">
                            <Image p="0 30px"
                                borderRadius="full" height="100px" src="https://bit.ly/sage-adebayo" alt="Segun Adebayo"
                                >
                            </Image>
                            <Image p="0 30px"
                               borderRadius="full" height="100px" src="https://bit.ly/sage-adebayo" alt="Segun Adebayo"
                                >
                            </Image>
                            <Image p="0 30px"
                                borderRadius="full" height="100px" src="https://bit.ly/sage-adebayo" alt="Segun Adebayo"
                                >
                            </Image>
                            <Image p="0 30px"
                                borderRadius="full" height="100px" src="https://bit.ly/sage-adebayo" alt="Segun Adebayo"
                                >
                            </Image>
                        </Flex>
                    </Box>
                </Flex>
                <Flex justifyContent="space-around" mt="67px" mb="80px" >
                    <Box textAlign="center" > 
                        <Flex 
                            p="0 70px"
                            alignItems="center"
                            width="384px"
                            height="79px"
                            backgroundColor="#FFFFFF"
                            boxShadow= "0px 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.19)"
                            borderRadius= "9px"
                        >
                        <Text
                            fontWeight= "500"
                            fontSize= "18px"
                            lineHeight= "21px"
                            textAlign= "center"
                        >
                                Uma equipe
                        </Text>
                            
                        </Flex>
                    </Box>
                </Flex> 
            </Box>
        </Box>
    );
}
